Jones eventually stopped Walker, sadly putting her in jail. Ducasse heard a knock at the door and opened it to Jones. She handed him to key to [[Alias Investigations]] and did not say a word. Ducasse watched her walk away, leaving [[Hell's Kitchen]]. He then looked at Alias Investigations, realizing that it was his now.{{Ref|JJ313}}

