*'''Master Investigator''': Under the reluctant tutelage of his boss [[Jessica Jones]], Ducasse became an extremely talented investigator, impressing fellow investigator [[Pryce Cheng]]. He managed to seek out information for [[Jeri Hogarth]] on her associates [[Linda Chao]] and [[Steven Benowitz]], choosing to lure out secrets while staying on their good sides. Ducasse also aided Walker in locating [[Karl Malus]] through the location data that was left on images taken from Jones' cellphone.
